Package: github-rdp-toolkit
Version: 9.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: usekarne <usekarne@users.noreply.github.com>
Section: net
Priority: optional
Depends: bash, openssh-client, curl, python3, freerdp2-x11
Recommends: xfce4, xrdp
Suggests: cloudflared, docker.io, vagrant
Description: GitHub RDP Mega Toolkit v9.0
 Cross-platform RDP session manager with Serveo/localhost.run/Cloudflare
 tunnel support. Spins up Windows or Linux RDP sessions on GitHub Actions
 runners, fetches credentials via artifact, and connects with xfreerdp.
 .
 Features:
  * Multi-provider tunnel failover (Serveo -> localhost.run -> Cloudflare)
  * 25+ GitHub Actions workflows
  * Cross-platform: Kali, Ubuntu, Windows, Android (Termux)
  * .deb/.msi package builders
  * Virtual environments (Docker, Vagrant, Podman)
  * Auto-config generation
  * Password rotation, health monitoring, notifications
  * Client CLI suite (Python, Bash, PowerShell)
